worth, Surrey|Wentworth]] in Virginia Water\n**[[Guildford#Westborough|Westborough]] in Guildford\n**[[West End, Esher|West End]] in Esher\n**West Ewell in Ewell\n**[[Westfield, Surrey|Westfield]] in Woking\n**[[Weston Green]] in Thames Ditton\n**[[Whiteley Village]] in Hersham\n**[[Normandy, Surrey|Willey Green]] in Normandy\n**Wonersh Common in Wonersh\n**Woodbridge Hill in Guildford\n**[[Woodhatch]] in Reigate\n**[[Reigate#Wray Common|Wray Common]] in Reigate and Redhill\n**[[Normandy, Surrey|Wyke]] in Normandy\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{List of places in England}}\n{{Surrey|state=expanded}}\n\n==External links==\n:[http://toolserver.org/~para/cgi-bin/kmlexport?article=List_of_places_in_Surrey&linksfrom=1&redir=google ''Map of places in Surrey compiled from this list'']\n\n[[Category:Lists of places in English counties|Surrey]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Surrey| ]]\n[[Category:Surrey-related lists|Places]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Location map many\n| United Kingdom Surrey\n| width       = 320 \n| float       = \n| border      = black\n| caption     = Major towns and conurbations in Surrey\n| alt         = \n| relief      = \n| AlternativeMap = \n| <!--first label/marker -->\n| label1      =  Guildford\n| label1_size =  60\n| position1   =  \n| background1 =  #FEFEE9\n| mark1       =  <!-- or: mark -->\n| mark1size   =  <!-- or: marksize -->\n| link1       =  Guildford\n| lat1_deg    =  51\n| lat1_min    =  14\n| lat1_sec    =  11.9\n| lat1_dir    =  N\n| lon1_deg    =  0\n| lon1_min    =  34\n| lon1_sec    =  13.1\n| lon1_dir    =  W\n| label2      = Woking\n| label2_size = 60\n| position2   =\n| background2 =  #FEFEE9\n| mark2       = \n| mark2size   = \n| link2       = Woking\n| lat2_deg    = 51\n| lat2_min    = 18\n| lat2_sec    = 58.32\n| lat2_dir    = N\n| lon2_deg    = 0\n| lon2_min    = 33\n| lon2_sec    = 39.6\n| lon2_dir    = W\n| label3      = Epsom and Ewell\n| label3_size = 60\n| position3   =\n| backgrou