ndon Borough of Lambeth|Lambeth]], [[List of districts in the London Borough of Merton|Merton]], [[List of districts in the London Borough of Southwark|Southwark]], [[List of districts in the London Borough of Sutton|Sutton]] and [[List of districts in the London Borough of Wandsworth|Wandsworth]].  Some of these parts of the [[historic counties of England|historic county]] lay, until its 1996 official disestablishment, in a fourth definition of Surrey, the [[postal counties of England|postal county]].\n\nBordering Counties (West-East):\n\n[[Berkshire]], [[Hampshire]], [[West Sussex]], [[Greater London]], [[East Sussex]] and [[Kent]].\n\nRailway Companies in Surrey (West-East):\n\n[[Great Western Railway (train operating company)|Great Western Railway]], [[South Western Railway (train operating company)|South Western Railway]], [[Thameslink]], [[Southern (Govia Thameslink Railway)|Southern]], [[Southeastern (train operating company)|Southeastern]] and [[Gatwick Express]]\n\n<!-- per [[WP:LIST|Lists policy]]: parks, hills, and geographic other features are not included, hence Newlands Corner, Ranmore Common, Hurtwood, Leith Hill, Box Hill, Chobham Common, Staple Hill, Gibbet Hill and Devil's Punch Bowl are not mentioned here.-->\n\n{{compact ToC|side=yes|top=yes|num=yes}}\n\n==A==\n[[Image:AddlestoneCrouchOak.jpg|thumb|The Crouch Oak Tree, [[Addlestone]]]]\n*[[Abinger]], [[Addlestone]], [[Albury, Surrey|Albury]], [[Alfold]], [[Artington]], [[Ash, Surrey|Ash]], [[Ash Vale]], [[Ashford, Surrey|Ashford]], [[Ashtead, Surrey|Ashtead]]\n**Abbotswood in Guildford\n**[[Abinger Common]] and [[Abinger Hammer]] in Abinger\n**[[Ashford, Surrey|Ashford Common]] in Ashford\n**Ambleside in Walton-on-Thames\n**[[Ashley Park]] in Walton-on-Thames\n\n==B==\n*[[Badshot Lea]], [[Bagshot, Surrey|Bagshot]], [[Banstead]], [[Betchworth]], [[Bisley, Surrey|Bisley]], [[Bletchingley]], [[Great Bookham|Bookham (Great and Little)]], [[Box Hill, Surrey|Box Hill]], [[Bramley, Surrey|Bramley]], [[Brockham, Surrey|Brockham]], [[Brookwood, Surrey|Brookwood]], [[Buckland, Surrey|Buckland]], [[Burgh Heath]], [[Burpham, Surrey|Burpham]], [[Burstow]], [[Busbridge]], [[Byfleet]]\n**[[Beacon Hill, Surrey|Beacon Hill]] in Haslemere\n**[[Capel, Surrey#Beare Green|Beare Green]] in Capel\n**[[Guildford#Bellfields|Bellfields]] in Guildford\n**[[Bramley, Surrey#Birtley Green|Birtley Green]] in Bramley\n**[[Wonersh#Blackheath|Blackheath]] in Wonersh\n**[[Blindley Heath]] in Godstone\n**[[Chobham#Penny Pot, Broadford and Castle Green|Broadford]] in Chobham\n**[[Brook, Surrey|Brook]] in Wormley\n**Brooklands in Weybridge\n**Brookwood Heath in Brookwood\n**[[Burntcommon]] in Send\n**[[Burwood Park]] in Hersham and Walton-on-Thames\n\n==C==\n[[File:Chertrsey Road2.jpg|thumbnail|Pyrcroft Road, [[Chertsey]]]]\n[[Image:FarnhamCst.png|thumb|Castle Street, [[Farnham]]]]\n*[[Camberley]], [[Capel, Surrey|Capel]], [[Caterham]], [[Chaldon]], [[Charlwood]], [[Chertsey]], [[Chiddingfold]], [[Chilworth, Surrey|Chilworth]], [[Chipstead, Surrey|Chipstead]], [[Chobham, Surrey|Chobham]], [[Churt]], [[Claygate]], [[Cobham, Surrey|Cobham]], [[Compton, Guildford|Compton (Borough of Guildford)]], [[Compton, Waverley|Compton (Waverley)]], [[Cranleigh]]\n**[[Caterham on the Hill]] and [[Caterham Valley]] in Caterham\n**Castle End in Egham\n**[[Chobham#Penny Pot, Broadford and Castle Green|Castle Green]] in Chobham\n**[[Catteshall]] in Godalming\n**Charlotteville in Guildford\n**[[Shepperton#Charlton|Charlton]] in Shepperton\n**[[Coldharbour, Surrey|Coldharbour]] in Newdigate\n**Cooper's Hill in Englefield Green\n**[[Newdigate#Cudworth|Cudworth]] in Newdigate\n\n==D==\n*[[Deepcut]], [[Dockenfield]] (part), [[Dorking]], [[Dormansland, Surrey|Dormansland]], [[Downside, Surrey|Downside]], [[Dunsfold]]\n\n==E==\n[[Image:Englegreenchurch.jpg|thumb|Church & Mausolea at [[Englefield Green]].]]\n*[[East Clandon]], [[East Horsley]], [[East Molesey]], [[Effingham, Surrey|Effingham]], [[Egham]], Ellen's Green, 